page.title: 15BUTTERFLIES AND MOTHS
page.content:
Below is a list of butterflies and moths found and identified by Kathrine Tomlinson at either the caterpillar or adult stage of development between 17th April and 4th July 1985.
YELLOW TAIL MOTHS found on Hawthorn FIGURE OF EIGHT MOTH found on Hawthorn MAGPIE MOTHS found on Garden Euonymus HERALD MOTHS found on Lupin BRIGHTLINE BROWN EYED MOTH found on Lupin GARDEN TIGER MOTH found in field LACKEY MOTH found on Raspberries DRINKER MOTH found on Grass SMALL TORTOISESHELL BUTTERFLIES found on Nettles MULLEIN MOTH found on Mullein.
